snippet.title: Party Hard - Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Stop the party next door by any means in Party Hard, the stealth strategy game from tinyBuild and Pinokl Games. Coming to PS4 on April 26th! Follow tinyBuild on twitter - http://twitter.com/tinyBuild
